run-once.sh runs your tests once

Assumptions:
  - CMake 2.8 or later installed (probable works in 2.6, but not tested)
  - A working C++ enviroment
  - The GTest framework is in the directory gtest.
  
Instructions:

 Unix/Mac OS + Make:

   $ mkdir build
   $ cd build
   $ cmake ..
   $ ctest -VV

